FBIS4-29135 "dreas116_l_94003" FBIS-EAS-94-116 Daily Report 16 Jun 1994 Philippines Ramos Names New National Police Chief Ramos Names New National Police Chief BK1606054894 Quezon City Radio Filipinas in English 0230 GMT 16 Jun 94 BK1606054894 Quezon City Radio Filipinas English BFN [Text] President Ramos today named the next chief of the Philippine National Police [PNP]. He is Major General Ricaredo Sarmiento. Sarmiento will replace PNP Chief General Humberto Rodriguez, who will retire effective 8 July. The president said he has accepted Rodriguez's letter of retirement. Sarmiento's term will also take effect on 8 July.
